value.0: Shadow Guards wear matching obsidian robes, battle armor, and helmets. Although ceremonial, the black armor does not hamper movement or fighting. The armor bears design influences from the uniforms of the Death Watch of the Mandalore system, the Sun Guards of the Thyrsus system, and the Senate Guards of the old Galactic Republic.
